scenes.description: Promotional material for concert merchandise, specifically the HYTE x hololive Official Collectible Card set.
Ninomae Ina'nis delivers a pre-recorded message to the audience as an AmiAmi ambassador, expressing her excitement for the concert.
A slideshow of numerous fan messages and illustrations cheering for the hololive English 3rd Concert members.
Promotional poster for the upcoming hololive English -Advent- 2nd Anniversary Live "On the Run!".
Promotional slide for Kureiji Ollie's "ZOM-RAID TIME" on the holoplus app.
Pre-concert waiting screen displaying the official hashtag #holoAllforOne and the concert cast.
Attention screen for visitors providing safety guidelines about flashing lights and cheering rules.
